Toxic Heavy Metals can cause your depersonalization, bipolar, mania, unexplained sadness, anxiety, OCD, depression, and so much more.  It is not who you are, you are not those ailments, symptoms, and conditions. 

You are more than those labels, and your true self is who your soul is and deep down inside your struggle is not your fault, you are a good person and it’s critical you know this.

Aloe Pineapple Juice Cooler

Ingredients: 

2 cups pineapple juice (or orange juice if you prefer)
2 tbsp (or 2-4” of aloe vera inner gel)* 
3 mint leaves 
1 lime, juiced
1/2 cup water
